manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Oyuiasle SD Card Reader for iPhone,iPad and Trail Cameras. Oyuiasle SD card reader, easily and simply uploads photos and videos from camera roll to iPhone, is ideal for iPhone users.

This SD card reader plugs into your iPhone and lets you easily view photos and videos from a variety of camera memory cards and upload files to your iPhone anytime, anywhere. Two-way transfer : The SD Card Reader for iPhone supports two-way transfer,from SD card to iPhone or iPhone to SD memory cards. Raw files : The SD Card Reader supports standard photo formats including JPEG,RAW,and 4K video formats including H.264 and MPEG-4. High-Speed : Fast transfer speed,ensures high-speed syncing for raw photos,4k videos,and more. Play and Play : The SD Card Reader does not require third-party apps,uses the iOS built-in Files app,and supports play videos.
Double slot design. SD/ MicroSD, SDHC/ MicroSDHC, SDXC/ MicroSDXC cards from Digital Camera/Dash Cam/Trail Cam are supported.

How to read & transfer in your iPhone ? up to iOS 13 and later: Simply insert the SD card into the slot and go to 'Files' app(iOS built-in app, not third-party software) , and go to 'NoName' (or Untiled, which is the name of your memory card) selection to select your files from the SD card. Then move the files as needed onto iPad or iPhone. up to iOS 9.2 and later: All you do is insert your SD card, go to the Photos app, and click on imports. From there you can select whatever photos you would like to import.

Broadly compatible. ✔ Cards Compatibility Compatible With SD, SDHC, SDXC, RS-MMSC, MicroSD, MicroSDHC, Micro SDXC. ✔ Compatible With iPhone Compatible With iPhone 5/5S/5C/SE, 6/6S/6 Plus/6S Plus, 7/7S/7 Plus/7S Plus, 8/8S/8 Plus/8S Plus, X/XS/XR/XS Max, 11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max, 12/12 mini/12 Pro/12 Pro Max, 13/13 mini/13 Pro/13 Pro Max,14/14 Pro/14 Pro Max/14 Plus, 15/15 Plus/15 Pro/15 Pro Max.. ✔ Compatible With iPad Compatible With iPad 10.2-inch 9th Gen / 8th Gen / 7th Gen, iPad 9.7-inch 6th Gen / 5th Gen, iPad Pro 12.9-inch 2nd Gen/1st Gen, iPad Pro 10.5-inch, iPad Pro 9.7-inch, iPad Air 10.5-inch 3rd Gen, iPad Air 9.7-inch 2th Gen / 1st Gen, iPad mini 7.9-inch 5th Gen / 4th Gen / 3th Gen / 2th Gen ✔ Special Feature Plug and Play! reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works great !!! BUY it
reviews.reviewText: Not only does it work seamlessly, I was able to play pirated movies on my I Pad. And the device accepts the Apple cable for charging. If it breaks or stops working for any reason, I will update.Obviously, the player Apple uses to view video files will not play every type of file. .mkv files won't play for instance on my I Pad. If you had an .mkv file - for example - convert it to a file type that works - like mp4. Many websites online provide this service for free.Also, the unique plug Apple has for all it's devices are prone to need of regular replacement. This type of cord more often than other cables no longer function after only a few months with cheap cords... and this is a very cheap cord. Once plugged into your Apple device, I wouldn't recommend not unplugging and plugging back into. And, when the plug no longer functions, the entire product here will become useless.

reviews.reviewText: I always reserve my judgment on electronic gear until it lasts for a while. I just received this device and everything I’ve tried on it has worked so far. I did try to put an older large SD card in it, and there was not a slot large enough to hold the older SD card. it works fine with the microSD card and works on my Apple devices. I’m using it to access pictures and videos from my DJI drone. It gives me a fast and efficient way to get access to these files which can be large. I could give 5 stars but I like to reserve that for products that stand the test of time.
